{"tid":811860,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【樓爆2018】大跌先兆！搞限售噱頭！劏盤每名買家最多可購2伙！！！","createTime":"2018-09-09T07:29:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-09T07:41:39.000Z","uid":43146,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"29f392ae59b81be3ef403ee390b0188d4de671a7","tid":811860,"uid":43146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T07:29:58.000Z","msg":"&lt;匯港通訊&gt; 恒地(00012)旗下西營盤「藝里坊&bull;1號」公布銷售安排，恒基物業代理營業(二)部總經理韓家輝指，項目已收約180票，日內將公布銷售安排，計劃下周三售50伙，下周二下午3時截票，每名買家最多可購2伙。<br />\n<br />\n利嘉閣地產總裁廖偉強表示，中小型單位今年以來大受市場追捧，無論自住及投資均是市場上炙手可熱的選擇。而今年截至9月5日，港島區實用面積在400平方呎或以下的一手住宅買賣登記已突破一千宗，共錄得1029宗，已較2017年全年的573宗激增近八成，反映此類單位確實大受市場歡迎。(SC)"},{"pid":"42c73c4c29da0d0eea01a7664b39833c8ada1e26","tid":811860,"uid":75589,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T07:38:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9443817b1f121b7a59df9d9cebf31f870fd62f08","tid":811860,"uid":43146,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"42c73c4c29da0d0eea01a7664b39833c8ada1e26","tid":811860,"uid":75589,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T07:38:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T07:39:34.000Z","msg":"淡軍投資專家話而家新盤低溢價<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔入票正戇鳩"},{"pid":"a48322ce79d62bf3f7ea0d2b1ac255471fc89614","tid":811860,"uid":75589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T07:40:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cdf25b01be0c713038d2dc7227505a889a43d4ae","tid":811860,"uid":43146,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a48322ce79d62bf3f7ea0d2b1ac255471fc89614","tid":811860,"uid":75589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9443817b1f121b7a59df9d9cebf31f870fd62f08","tid":811860,"uid":43146,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"42c73c4c29da0d0eea01a7664b39833c8ada1e26","tid":811860,"uid":75589,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T07:38:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-